title: For Sale/Trade:  **ATTENTION ALL ARMSLIST SELLERS AND BUYERS!!**
postcontent:
This is for all ARMSLIST.com sellers:

If you are not willing to accept trades, please do not make the listing as a For Sale/Trade listing! It is very MISLEADING and and I am going to encourage all potential customers who were looking to make a trade to flag these listings for misleading or otherwise untruthful information.
